ike":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得視乎情況英書中教最理想<br />\n三大神科用返英文<br />\n因為基本上佢地中小學已經係英書英教<br />\n就算用英文都唔會有問題<br />\n但普通科有時連教的人的英文水平都唔多掂<br />\n學生的英文水平又唔多掂<br />\n結果就係大家都用緊自己唔熟悉的語言溝通<br />\n可能只係接收到50%的知識"},{"pid":"c29c1bf6a4010e9a551aebd9a399fc5147271ae5","tid":1016943,"uid":29625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"要幾無知先問得出<br />\n你咪試下用中文讀 讀完連啲paper都睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ddfc1036a0a5a875f1998e72730deb8af03ff","tid":1016943,"uid":134321,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ae87294d2e49ab5feec9eb3bca6991f0a5cf190","tid":1016943,"uid":81424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"中文學術界唔計大陸得返臺灣同香港<br />\n大陸太鳩<br />\n臺灣同香港太細<br />\n唔夠支撐起一個完整嘅學術圈子"},{"pid":"8e4300307118d42ecd4dd8e54972ca1326c61205","tid":1016943,"uid":51453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae87294d2e49ab5feec9eb3bca6991f0a5cf190","tid":1016943,"uid":81424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"中文學術界唔計大陸得返臺灣同香港<br />\n大陸太鳩<br />\n臺灣同香港太細<br />\n唔夠支撐起一個完整嘅學術圈子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"咁點解日本得？"},{"pid":"9d21ceab7321fa440fddfb8c8658b6e4b7be1c0a","tid":1016943,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e4300307118d42ecd4dd8e54972ca1326c61205","tid":1016943,"uid":51453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae87294d2e49ab5feec9eb3bca6991f0a5cf190","tid":1016943,"uid":81424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"中文學術界唔計大陸得返臺灣同香港<br />\n大陸太鳩<br />\n臺灣同香港太細<br />\n唔夠支撐起一個完整嘅學術圈子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"咁點解日本得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"日本有成億人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk